    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演傲慢自大的飞车党女孩Lucky，与恶魔及黑暗军团展开战斗。她被迫收割灵魂，永无解脱。她将摧毁魔鬼派来折磨她的每一个恶魔和亡灵，让它们永远只能在路边搭车求生。皮夹克、油头、机油与汽油——这是一个充满浓厚油污、以时速100英里屠杀的世界。.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/6d3260d5566b52dba05f8bdb76a638ee.poster.avif?t=1757580879\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/6d3260d5566b52dba05f8bdb76a638ee.webm?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/6d3260d5566b52dba05f8bdb76a638ee.mp4?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冲向路之尽头</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为“公路死神”，你被束缚在命丧之地的高速公路上，永无止境地收割灵魂。然而，在方向盘后，你是不可忽视的力量，挥舞你的闪亮霰弹枪，击溃所有“恶魔”派来的魔鬼和亡灵，冲向路之尽头。在每一次逃离地狱的尝试中，你会变得更强大，并揭开更多关于自己和这个世界的真相。.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/abb008089e743174d9bb23a51091f710.poster.avif?t=1757580879\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/abb008089e743174d9bb23a51091f710.webm?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/abb008089e743174d9bb23a51091f710.mp4?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能、力量与补给站</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要停下来喘口气？在路上做出战略性停留，访问其他“公路死神”，他们会借你力量，帮助你走得更远。选择关键盟友以获取新的技能、能力和技巧，这些组合将打造强大的角色，让恶魔也闻风丧胆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/e049c4b91af895827fbbb3437603bca5.poster.avif?t=1757580879\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/e049c4b91af895827fbbb3437603bca5.webm?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/e049c4b91af895827fbbb3437603bca5.mp4?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为可重玩游戏量身定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次尝试逃离束缚都是全新的体验。探索更多关于“死神”同伴、阻碍你前进的敌人，甚至你自己的秘密。那些之前被你打得落花流水的敌人会记住你。前往废品收购站，购买永久升级装备，强化你的座驾，为复仇而战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/d70072f45b020e531e4b8ee1ff627ed2.poster.avif?t=1757580879\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/d70072f45b020e531e4b8ee1ff627ed2.webm?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238240/extras/d70072f45b020e531e4b8ee1ff627ed2.mp4?t=1757580879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恶魔的诡计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“恶魔”总是先你一步，她不断调整策略，派遣数量和实力各异的敌人阻挠你的逃亡。她密切注视着你的一举一动，精心策划着让你陷入绝境的阴谋。 </p>",
